etIterations`: Controls precision (actual iterations = √targetIterations)\n- `maxRegions`: Maximum regions to select (cardinality constraint k)\n- `roundingCandidates`: Number of rounding candidates for min-energy selection\n- `qualityWeight`: Weight for quality-based utility\n- `coverageWeight`: Weight for spatial coverage utility\n\n## Proven Properties (FAA.lean, ContinuousGreedy.lean)\n\n- Achieves (1 - 1/e - O(1/√T)) approximation\n- In √T iterations instead of T\n- Min-energy rounding is deterministic and noise-resilient\n","info":{"dataDeclType":"newtype","declType":"data","roles":[],"typeArguments":[]},"kind":null,"sourceSpan":{"end":[161,4],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/GPU/FrameState/Allocation/Types.purs","start":[154,1]},"title":"FAAAllocationConfig"},{"children":[],"comments":"Create FAA allocation config with sensible defaults.\n\n## Real-Time Defaults (60fps target)\n\n- targetIterations: 100 → √100 = 10 actual iterations\n- roundingCandidates: 20 → fast min-energy selection\n- qualityWeight: 0.7 → prioritize render quality\n- coverageWeight: 0.3 → secondary coverage objective\n","info":{"declType":"value","type":{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"Function"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"Int"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"Function"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"Int"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","GPU","FrameState","Allocation","Types"],"FAAAllocationConfig"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"}],"tag":"TypeApp"}},"kind":null,"sourceSpan":{"end":[178,59],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/GPU/FrameState/Allocation/Types.purs","start":[178,1]},"title":"mkFAAAllocationConfig"},{"children":[],"comments":"Get target iterations from config.\n","info":{"